hadiths[8]{hadithnumber,text}:
5467,mere yahan aik ladka paida hua to main usey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska naam Ibrahim rakha aur khajoor ko apne daanton se narm karke usey chataayaa aur uske liye barkat ki dua ki phir mujhey de diya. ye abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sabse badey ladkey they.
5468,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik naya paida hua bachcha laya gaya taake aap uski tehneek kar dein. us bachche ne aap ke uper peshab kar diya, aap ne is par pani baha diya."
5469,"Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein unke pet mein they. unhon-ne kaha ke phir main (jab hijrat ke liye) nikli to waqt wilaadat qareeb tha. Madina Munawra pahunch kar maine pehli manzil Quba mein ki aur yahin Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) paida ho gaey, main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bachche ko lekar hazir hui aur usey aap ki god mein rakh diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor talab farmai aur usey chabaayaa aur bachche ke munh mein apna thook daal diya. chunanche pehli cheez jo us bachcha ke pet mein gaee wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka thook tha phir aap ne khajoor se tehneek ki aur uske liye barkat ki dua farmai. ye sabse pahlaa bachcha Islam main (hijrat ke baad Madina Munawra mein) paida hua. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) us se bahut khush huey kyonke ye afawaah phailaaii ja rahi thi ke yahudiyon ne tum (muslmaanon) par jaadoo kar diya hai. isliye tumharey yahan ab koi bachcha paida nahi hoga."
5470,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ladka bimar tha. abu-Talha kahin bahar gaey huey they ke bachche ka intiqal ho gaya. jab wo (thakey maandey) wapas aaey to puchha ke bachcha kaisa hai? unki biwi Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo pahley se zyada sukoon ke sath hai, phir biwi ne unke samney khana rakha aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne khana khaayaa. iske baad unhon-ne unke sath ham-bistarii ki phir jab farigh huey to unhon-ne kaha ke bachche ko dafn kar do. subah hui to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko waaqie ki itlaa di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tum ne raat ham-bistarii bhi ki thi? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ''aey Allaah! un donon ko barkat ata farmaa.'' phir unke yahan aik bachcha paida hua to mujh se abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke usey hifazat ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley jao. chunanche bachcha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laey aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne bachche ke sath kuchh khajoorein bhejiin, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachche ko liya aur malum farmaya ke iske sath koi cheez bhi hai? logon ne kaha ke ji haan khajoorein hain. aap ne usey lekar chabaayaa aur phir usey apne munh mein nikal kar bachche ke munh mein rakh diya aur us se bachche ki tehneek ki aur uska naam Abdullah rakha."
5471,"bachche ka aqeeqa karna chahiye aur Hajjaj-bin Minhal ne kaha, unse Hammaad-bin-Salma ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Ayub sakhtiyan , Qatada , Hisham bin Hassan aur Habib bin Shahid un charon ne khabar di, unhein Muhammad-bin Sirin ne aur unhein Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. aur kai logon ne bayan kya, unse Aasim bin Sulaiman aur Hisham bin Hassan ne, unse Hafsa binte- Sirin ne, unse Rubaab-binte-Salee' ne, unse Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unhon-ne marfooan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai aur uski riwayat Yazeed bin Ibrahim tastarii ne ki, unse Muhammad-bin Sirin ne aur unse Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna qaul mauqoofan (ghair marfooa) zikr kya."
5472,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ladkey ke sath uska aqeeqa laga hua hai isliye uski taraf se janwar zabah karo aur usse baal door karo (sar mundaa 2 ya khatna karo)."
5473,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (Islam mein) (faraa') aur) عتيرة ( nahi hain. (faraa') ( ontni ke) sabse pahley bachcha ko kehtey they jisey (jaahiliyat mein) log apne buton ke liye zabah kartey they aur) عتيرة ( ko rajab mein zabah kya jata tha.
5474,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) faraa' (aur ( عتيرة ( (Islam mein) nahi hain. bayan kya ke) faraa' ( sabse pahley bachche ko kehtey they jo unke yahan (oontnii se) paida hota tha, usey wo apne buton ke naam par zabah kartey they aur) عتيرة ( wo qurbani jisey wo rajab mein kartey they (aur uski khaal darakht par daal detey ( ."
